1. &quot;Straight&quot; 
2. &quot;Volcano Girls&quot;
3. &quot;Don't Make Me Prove It&quot; 
4. &quot;Awesome&quot;
5. &quot;One Last Time&quot; 
6. &quot;With David Bowie&quot; 
7. &quot;Benjamin&quot;
